I can never seem to find 'the right pants' they either fit my legs and not my hips, or fit my hips and not my legs...whatever. Nomatter how much I love shopping...it can still be a major pain in the boo-tay. 

Do you ever feel like no one's there for you at all...even if you have a close friend standing by you...it seems like they don't care and would just rather be doing their own thing. My mood'll probably change by tomorrow...but for now I'm just feeling lame as heck. 

...I hate bad moods...

Gosh I can't believe that summer is officially over...no more sleeping in. It's back to getting up at 5:30, going to school, then coming home to chores and homework. I wish summer could last forever. It'll be nice to see everyone again...but I can do that outside of school if I really want to. I'm not really looking foreward to any of my classes...especially health care...I'm so pissed that they put me in that class. Especially when I wanted Journalism. It was a pretty good summer...too bad it's come to an end.
